p://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:14:\"Benjamin Rojas\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:9811:\"<p>Are you losing traffic due to broken links? Do you know if you have any broken links?</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Surprisingly, most links on the web <em>are</em> broken. Thereâ€™s even a name for it: <strong>link rot</strong>.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>So, why does it matter?</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Broken links make it hard for users to find what theyâ€™re looking for. That drives visitors away. And when you lose visitors, you lose conversions and sales.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>A broken link can also make a page invisible to search engines. That means zero traffic.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>But who has time to check every web page and link on a website? Ideally, site owners should check for broken links regularly. But that makes the task even more time-consuming.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Thatâ€™s why we decided to create a fast solution that even a beginner can use.</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"is-layout-flow wp-block-group aioseo-table-of-contents has-theme-info-background-color has-background\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<p>In This Article</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-aioseo-table-of-contents\"><ul><li><a href=\"#aioseo-find-and-fix-broken-links-easily\">Find and Fix Broken Links, Easily</a><ul><li><a href=\"#aioseo-semi-weekly-scans\">Semi-Weekly Scans</a></li><li><a href=\"#aioseo-additional-features\">Additional Features</a></li></ul></li><li><a href=\"#aioseo-control-which-types-of-pages-are-scanned\">Control Which Types of Pages are Scanned</a></li><li><a href=\"#aioseo-scanning-the-right-way\">Scanning &#8211; the Right Way</a><ul><li><a href=\"#aioseo-avoid-being-blacklisted\">Avoid Being Blacklisted</a></li></ul></li><li><a href=\"#aioseo-how-to-get-broken-link-checker-by-aioseo\">How to Get Broken Link Checker by AIOSEO</a></li></ul></div>\n</div></div>\n\n\n\n<h2 id=\"aioseo-find-and-fix-broken-links-easily\">Find and Fix Broken Links, Easily</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Weâ€™re excited to announce our brand new, standalone <strong><a href=\"https://aioseo.com/pricing-broken-link-checker/\" title=\"Broken Link Checker plugin\">Broken Link Checker plugin</a></strong>.</p>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li>This plugin <strong><em>scans</em></strong> all the links on your site.</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Then it <strong><em>lists</em></strong> all broken links and provides an <strong>easy way to fix</strong> them.</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<p>You donâ€™t even need to open any web pages.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Just click <strong>Edit URL</strong> to replace a broken link â€“ right inside the plugin.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"523\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/fix-broken-link-1024x523.png\" alt=\"broken link checker edit url\" class=\"wp-image-174472\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/fix-broken-link-1024x523.png 1024w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/fix-broken-link-300x153.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/fix-broken-link-768x392.png 768w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/fix-broken-link-1536x784.png 1536w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/fix-broken-link-2048x1046.png 2048w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/fix-broken-link-600x306.png 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/fix-broken-link-118x60.png 118w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/fix-broken-link-176x90.png 176w\" sizes=\"100vw\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>You can also edit the anchor text at the same time.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"aioseo-semi-weekly-scans\">Semi-Weekly Scans</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>The Broken Link Checker plugin automatically scans your site <strong>every 3 days</strong>. So thereâ€™s no need to worry about missing broken links 