ogle understand your content better and match your business to relevant search queries.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"aioseo-step-2-check-your-seo-analysis\">Step 2: Check Your Homepage SEO</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Next, review your homepage for improvements.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>To do this, in the WordPress admin bar, navigate to <strong>AIOSEO Â» SEO Analysis.</strong></p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"517\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/aioseo-seo-analysis-1024x517.png\" alt=\"aioseo seo analysis menu item\" class=\"wp-image-170734\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/aioseo-seo-analysis-1024x517.png 1024w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/aioseo-seo-analysis-300x151.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/aioseo-seo-analysis-768x388.png 768w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/aioseo-seo-analysis-1536x776.png 1536w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/aioseo-seo-analysis-2048x1034.png 2048w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/aioseo-seo-analysis-600x303.png 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/aioseo-seo-analysis-119x60.png 119w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/aioseo-seo-analysis-178x90.png 178w\" sizes=\"100vw\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Now, you&#8217;ll see your website&#8217;s overall <strong>Site Score</strong>.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"520\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/aioseo-site-score-1024x520.png\" alt=\"aioseo site score\" class=\"wp-image-170735\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/aioseo-site-score-1024x520.png 1024w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/aioseo-site-score-300x152.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/aioseo-site-score-768x390.png 768w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/aioseo-site-score-1536x780.png 1536w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/aioseo-site-score-2048x1040.png 2048w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/aioseo-site-score-600x305.png 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/aioseo-site-score-118x60.png 118w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/aioseo-site-score-177x90.png 177w\" sizes=\"100vw\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>And beneath that is a <strong>Complete SEO Checklist</strong>.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"643\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/aioseo-complete-seo-checklist-1024x643.png\" alt=\"aioseo complete seo checklist\" class=\"wp-image-170737\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/aioseo-complete-seo-checklist-1024x643.png 1024w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/aioseo-complete-seo-checklist-300x188.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/aioseo-complete-seo-checklist-768x482.png 768w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/aioseo-complete-seo-checklist-1536x964.png 1536w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/aioseo-complete-seo-checklist-2048x1286.png 2048w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/aioseo-complete-seo-checklist-600x377.png 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/aioseo-complete-seo-checklist-96x60.png 96w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/aioseo-complete-seo-checklist-143x90.png 143w\" sizes=\"100vw\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>This checklist provides an analysis of your <strong>homepage </strong>with recommended action items. These are sorted by:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li>Important Issues (flagged in red)</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Recommended Improvements</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Good results.</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<p>We recommend tackling <strong>Important Issues</strong> first.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Clicking on an item will provide the specific action steps to take.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>For example, this checklist item tells us that our homepage is missing a meta description. And it provides a button to click that will take you to the area you need to add the description to.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"605\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/aioseo-meta-description-missing-1-1024x605.png\" alt=\"aioseo edit meta description\" class=\"wp-image-170739\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/aioseo-meta-description-missing-1-1024x605.png 1024w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/aioseo-meta-description-missing-1-300x177.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/aioseo-meta-description-missing-1-768x454.png 768w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/aioseo-meta-description-missing-1-1536x908.png 1536w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/aioseo-meta-description-missing-1-2048x1211.png 2048w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/aioseo-meta-description-missing-1-600x355.png 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/aioseo-meta-description-missing-1-101x60.png 101w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/aioseo-meta-description-missing-1-152x90.png 152w\" sizes=\"100vw\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"aioseo-learn-to-optimize-your-content\">Step 3: Learn to Optimize Your Content</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>When you finish working through the items in your SEO Analysis report, we recommend learning how to optimize individual web pages for SEO.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Youâ€™ll be surprised at how easy it is to learn this. To get started, explore these options:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li>Learn how to optimize <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/seo-title-tags/\">titles</a> and <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/how-to-write-meta-descriptions-for-seo/\">article descriptions</a></li>\n\n\n\n<li>Learn what a <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/docs/using-the-focus-keyphrase-to-analyze-your-content/\">focus keyword</a> is and how to use it.</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Learn what <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/how-to-add-rich-snippets-to-wordpress/\">rich snippets</a> are and how to create them.</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<p>And bookmark this blog to learn more.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"477\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/product-schema-1024x477.jpg\" alt=\"product schema rich snippet example\" class=\"wp-image-170741\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/product-schema-1024x477.jpg 1024w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/product-schema-300x140.jpg 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/product-schema-768x358.jpg 768w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/product-schema-600x280.jpg 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/product-schema-129x60.jpg 129w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/product-schema-193x90.jpg 193w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/product-schema.jpg 1180w\" sizes=\"100vw\" /><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\"><em>Above: These search results are rich snippets, made possible with <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/how-to-add-product-review-schema-in-wordpress/\" title=\"\">product schema</a> markup</em>.</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 id=\"aioseo-whats-next\">Whatâ€™s Next?</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>We hope this post helped you learn why having a Google Business Profile is important for your small business success and how you can make the most of it.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Also consider exploring <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/what-are-local-services-ads/\">Local Services Ads</a> and how to <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/how-to-use-a-wordpress-faq-block-to-boost-seo-and-get-more-traffic/\">get more traffic with FAQs</a>.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>If you found this article helpful, then please subscribe to our <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/c/AIOSEO\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"\">YouTube Channel</a>. Youâ€™ll find many more helpful tutorials there. You can also follow us on <a href=\"https://twitter.com/aioseopack\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"\">Twitter</a>, <a href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/company/aioseo/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"\">LinkedIn</a>, or <a href=\"https://facebook.com/aioseopack/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"\">Facebook</a> to stay in the loop.</p>The post <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/how-to-use-a-google-business-profile-to-imrpove-local-seo/\">How to Use a Google Business Profile to Boost Local SEO</a> first appeared on <a href=\"https://aioseo.com\">AIOSEO</a>.\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:82:\"https://aioseo.com/how-to-use-a-google-business-profile-to-imrpove-local-seo/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"1\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}}}s:27:\"http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom\";a:1:{s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:0:\"\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:3:{s:4:\"href\";s:24:\"https://aioseo.com/feed/\";s:3:\"rel\";s:4:\"self\";s:4:\"type\";s:19:\"application/rss+xml\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:44:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/syndication/\";a:2:{s:12:\"updatePeriod\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:9:\"\n	hourly	\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:15:\"updateFrequency\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:4:\"\n	1	\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}}}}}}}}s:4:\"type\";i:128;s:7:\"headers\";O:48:\"WpOrg\